    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Building a Custom CSV Renderer in Rails 3]]></title>
    <link href="http://beerlington.github.io/blog/2011/07/25/building-a-csv-renderer-in-rails-3/"/>
    <updated>2011-07-25T22:18:00-04:00</updated>
